Client Requirement Document
Project Name: TALEEM GYM – Member Mobile App (PWA)
Prepared For: Gym Members
Platform: Progressive Web App (PWA)
Version: 1.0
1.  Project Objective
To develop a simple and mobile-friendly application for gym members that allows them to:
• Check membership status
• Mark attendance
• Make payments
• Manage their membership easily
The focus is on speed, clarity, and ease of use.
2.  Platform Overview
The application will be delivered as a Progressive Web App (PWA):
• Accessible via browser
• Installable on mobile devices
• Optimized for Android users
• Fast loading with basic offline support
3.  Core Functional Requirements
3.1 Home Dashboard
The home screen will display:
• Membership status (Active / Expired / Frozen)
• Expiry date
• Remaining days
• Today’s attendance status
3.2 Attendance Management
Members will be able to:
• Mark attendance (QR scan)
• View attendance history
3.3 Membership & Payments
Membership Details
• View current plan
• View start and expiry dates
• View remaining validity
Membership Renewal
• Select membership plan
• Make payment online
• Automatic activation after successful payment
Payment History
• View all past transactions
• Includes:
o Amount
o Date
o Payment method
o Payment status
Freeze Membership
Members will have the option to temporarily pause their membership with certain amount (e.g.,
₹200/month).
Features:
• Freeze membership for a limited duration
• Resume membership when needed
Conditions:
• Available only for active memberships
• Maximum freeze duration will be predefined (e.g., up to 15 days)
• Freeze can be used limited times within a cycle
• Membership expiry will be extended based on freeze duration
• Attendance will not be allowed during freeze period
3.4 Notifications
Members will receive:
• Membership expiry reminders
• Payment confirmations
• Important updates from gym
3.5 Profile Management
Members can:
• View personal details
• Update basic information
• Logout securely
4.  Security Requirements
• Secure login for members
• Safe payment processing via trusted payment gateway
• No storage of sensitive payment details
5.  User Experience
• Clean and simple interface
• Mobile-first design
• Easy navigation
• Fast interaction for daily use
6.  Performance Requirements
• Load time under few seconds
• Smooth performance on standard Android devices
• Reliable payment and attendance updates
7.  Deliverables
• Fully functional Member PWA
• Mobile-optimized interface
• Online payment integration
• Backend system for data handling
• Deployment-ready application
8.  Future Enhancements (Optional)
• Workout plans for members
• Diet tracking
• Trainer interaction
• Advanced usage insights
9.  Approval
This document defines the agreed scope for the initial version.
Additional features will be considered as future enhancements.
